te. It is a purine alkaloid and a trimethylxanthine.", "source": {"type": "pubchem", "reference": "CID 2519", "section": null, "mineru_parsed": false}, "language": "en"}, {"type": "general_description", "content": "咖啡因是甲基黄嘌呤类中枢神经刺激剂，通过拮抗腺苷A1和A2A受体来提高警觉性，是全球使用最广泛的精神活性物质。", "source": {"type": "manual_curation", "reference": "CID 2519", "section": null, "mineru_parsed": false}, "language": "zh"}], "entity_relations": [{"subject": "Caffeine", "relation": "has_substructure", "object": "aromatic/cyclic ring system", "confidence": 0.9}, {"subject": "Caffeine", "relation": "derivative_of", "object": "drug-like molecule", "confidence": 0.85}], "alignment_metadata": {"alignment_confidence": 0.9, "validation_status": "automated_pass", "mineru_usage": [{"tool": "MinerU Open Source", "task": "使用 magic-pdf 本地解析Caffeine相关科学文献，提取结构化文本和图表", "input": "data/raw/papers/caffeine_studies.pdf", "output": "data/raw/parsed/caffeine_studies_parsed.json"}, {"tool": "MinerU API", "task": "Batch processed Caffeine literature via MinerU API, extracting pharmacological data tables", "input": "PubChem CID 2519", "output": "data/processed/molalign_dataset.jsonl"}], "created_at": "2026-05-30T20:17:38Z", "version": "2.0.0", "updated_at": "2026-05-30T20:35:16Z"}, "category": "Stimulant"}
